Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Belly button...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l don't know about this bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the times l've seen it, it's blurred out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have a feeling we've met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l moved here right after high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now l go to a local junior college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l decided to take a summer job at the Marine Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.15,0:01:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's for the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but more than that, l am hoping to meet a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's such a nice day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just can't picture myself doing those things with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder if l'll ever go to a hotel like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At one point l wanted to be a writer and tried to write a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wrote for a while, but then l realized it was just a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my name is Yoshiro Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm pretty serious, studying is my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope we can become friends this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty smooth, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's good to be outgoing, but make sure you get your work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Masato Fukuroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka and l are classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hang out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, l'm counting on both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, one moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, actually l am a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka is already working on that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chieri-chan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too good for Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at him, he's really going for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think l could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work, work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiring, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's tiring to have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what do you think about Chieri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about trying, she's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have Chieri-chan, but don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of cute girls on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're up for grabs, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Masato, you're still a virgin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect opportunity to meet a cute girl and get some action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l'm thinking about the mysterious girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in my dreams, not the girls down on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can l take your order?
