Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Table Three asked for another beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is you, Fukuroi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you did move here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...haven't changed since high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Chihiro Asaoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have l changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess you're a little taller, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you to my friend from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Masato Fukuroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just bumped into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Shingo Kunimi, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is staying at my house for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come and visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingo-san!
