Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is he the son of the city councilman...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he competed in the National Ski Championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you just hate his good looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, l'm not interested in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't stand a chance anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, boys will dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a fool would throw away his fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan's gotten so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe l said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''l guess you're a little taller, too.''
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had a crush on her all through high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now l realize that l've never gotten over her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become more beautiful than l've ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chihiro, l love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been waiting for this so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
