Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun, do you want me to put it in my mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
