Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a good dream or a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the likes of Masato annoy me even more.
