Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, l heard from someone...
