Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the cousin of that guy, the city councilman's son.
