Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you happy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legally, she could marry her cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they must be lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life's rough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the spring of your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Boss tells me this great news, then starts talking crap.
