Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Masato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on duty now, what is it?
