Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is taking a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Chieri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chieri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanted to keep it to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but l thought l'd share with my poor chick-less friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost...
