Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for a boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chieri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick it in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick your penis into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt feels good, Chieri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's none of my business, but you are on duty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean that wall and get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you might want to consider locking the door when you're in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really buying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is payday, so my pockets are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato, you pay for your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna do it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna do it with Chieri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l envy Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf only l had half the nerve he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot of summer left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sure something good will come your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Chihiro-chan and Mr. Handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, why don't you do something to take her from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you're so hung up on saving face and being cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll never get a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally met up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's get together, just the two of us, and reminisce...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that is, if you have time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when it's convenient for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what about your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder if Fukuroi-san's gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting strange, Fukuroi-kun, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l always know what to say in my fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't l come up with anything in real life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun, why did you move without telling anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was suddenly relocated by his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't want to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been thinking about you this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is sitting next me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close l can feel the warmth of her skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not a distant dream, but the closest person to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person l adore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi-san sure is a handsome guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even from a guy's standpoint, he's good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could never compare to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're handsome too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l read your story in high school and thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how amazing, to be able to write something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That story...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you wanted to be a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you were a great guy with a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:18:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you were a great guy with a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Oka's bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can suck better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're distracting me too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look Chieri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tastes funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l don't mind, because it came from the man l love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can give you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go for round two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka had sex with Chieri, just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, l screwed things up with Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, l will never go out with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a novelist with just an imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a really stupid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, boys will dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a fool would throw away his fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you're so hung up on saving face and being cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll never get a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll apologize Chihiro for that awkward parting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, l will ask her out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi-san, don't just watch, come join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one you want to try next?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.36,0:22:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is your change, 340 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-san seems to be getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.60,0:23:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.38,0:23:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is going back home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't see her for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've wanted to marry her since l was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.19,0:23:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Chihiro told me that she can only think of me as a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think maybe she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro's at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going for a walk before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think maybe she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.06,0:24:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-l've always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have always loved you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.97,0:24:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've waited for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.74,0:24:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So have l.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.04,0:24:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.64,0:24:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.65,0:24:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.09,0:25:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's shiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.99,0:25:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.32,0:25:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.49,0:25:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean your body is ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.49,0:25:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.20,0:25:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.90,0:25:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.93,0:25:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.07,0:25:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.11,0:26:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.14,0:26:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall l stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.04,0:26:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.54,0:26:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.15,0:26:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels good...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.85,0:26:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.89,0:26:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm starting to feel strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.16,0:26:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.19,0:26:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.96,0:26:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More, faster, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.60,0:26:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.03,0:26:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, more, more...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.00,0:26:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuroi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.84,0:26:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.74,0:26:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.95,0:26:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.16,0:26:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't hold back any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.03,0:26:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.70,0:27:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.51,0:27:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so lucky to have my first time be with my first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.02,0:27:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.69,0:27:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'll be a long distance relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.76,0:27:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.32,0:27:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.39,0:27:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and see me when you finish your new story.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.43,0:27:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.83,0:27:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.60,0:27:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel like our bodies connecting has connected our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.54,0:27:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got to finish my novel so l can see Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.35,0:27:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l once thought l didn't have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.75,0:27:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, l know l can write something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.69,0:27:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l'm sure it's because Chihiro has given me the strength.
